title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1995-06-04
description:
Set 1

Bertha, Wang Dang Doodle, Peggy-O, Queen Jane Approximately, Loose Lucy, Mama Tried*-> Mexicali Blues*, Lazy River Road, Cassidy (62 mins.)

Set 2

Here Comes Sunshine, Victim Or The Crime, Unbroken Chain, Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Space-> I Need A Miracle-> The Days Between-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace (91 mins.)

* Weir on acoustic

reviews.review_text: unbroken chain phil peaking in 95 phil really sings  the hell out of  unbroken chain  next  gem  days beteen  jerry take  his time down to the last sweet note  this must been hella weekend  i missed this run  i was thinking they had shot  there wad   boy was i wrong sounds like they still had more to give
